OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FP&O Ferries hits back at   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstaff pay cut claim        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, P&O Ferries has hit back at claims that
OL,6, it tried to get its new cheaper agency 
OL,7, staff to accept even lower wages.      
OL,9,FThe RMT Union said it received reports 
OL,10,Fof new workers at Dover being asked to 
OL,11,Fsign new contracts, replacing ones they
OL,12,Fhad signed weeks ago, on lower pay.    
OL,14,FIt reported P&O Ferries to the Maritime
OL,15,Fand Coastguard Agency, which ensured   
OL,16,Fthe new workers retained their wages.  
OL,18,FBut P&O Ferries told the BBC "no agency
OL,19,Fseafarers were asked to accept reduced 
OL,20,Fwages".                                
